::FZ::

FZ frowns, beginning to walk after Lady Hawk. "Hard feelings about what?" he asks, his hand near his gun.

The drones enter the room, moving the cages into seperate rooms that branch off the lab, the base scanning the creatures' DNA.




--- In nbwrpg@y..., "CYBERWOLF4" <cyberwolf4@p...> wrote:
> Lady Hawk exited passing a few maintenance drones as they hovered, rolled
> and squeaked toward FZ's location. "I hope there are no hard feelings." she
> said as she passed heading towards the exit door. "Maybe one day we'll work
> together under different circumstances." Although she knew that when Veratis
> had finished there would be no Alliance, Maximals, Predacons ect. She knew
> that when Veratis was done with these poor bots all would be one.
